data.description: Welcome to your dream abode!  This pristine and completely move-in ready 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath residence is a haven of comfort.  VA Buyers, assume the Sellers loan for a much lower interest rate.  Revel in the allure of brand-new fresh interior paint in all rooms and brand new flooring everywhere.  Home also features brand new kitchen cabinets with new granite countertops and backsplash, giving this home a contemporary and inviting ambiance.  The new vanity in the upstairs bathroom is a sleek and modern piece that complements the overall bathroom design. Move in and start creating cherished memories in this picture-perfect retreat. Made even more convenient with a nearby bus stop for effortless travel.  All 4 spacious bedrooms are upstairs.  The owners suite features a walk-in closet and the bathroom is equipped with double vanity.  Situated conveniently within a 15 minute car drive to Hartsfield Airport and close to bustling shopping centers and local restaurants, your daily commute and errands are a breeze. Enjoy easy and quick access to the freeway, public transportation and Marta trains.  Your ideal home awaits you and is ready to embrace your unique story.  Schedule your appointment today, before it's gone tomorrow. Some of the pictures have been virtually staged.  IF THE LISTING AGENT SHOWS AT THE INITIAL SHOWING, THE BUYERS AGENTS CO-0P IS REDUCED TO 2%
